-- U.K. to Sell 12.3 Million Spot Phase 3 Carbon Permits This Year
-- B y   A l e s s a n d r o   V i t e l l i
-- 2012-10-29T09:47:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-29/u-k-to-sell-12-3-million-spot-phase-3-carbon-permits-this-year.html
The U.K. will sell a total of 12.3
million Phase 3 spot European Union carbon permits in two
auctions on Nov. 21 and Dec. 5, according to ICE Futures  Europe .  The sales will take place from 8 a.m. to 10 a.m. London
time on the ICE Futures exchange. The bourse will also sell a
total of 7 million EU aviation permits in two auctions on Nov.
26 and Dec. 10.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alessandro Vitelli in London at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Verdonck at 
 rverdonck@bloomberg.net  